I had four cats who ate hard food &amp; one of them was slowly losing
weight.  Took him to the vet.  One of his upper fangs was loose &amp;
causing pain when he tried to eat. I bought soft food to 'fatten him up'
before dental work.

When I served the soft food, he wolfed down the whole can.  I felt so
guilty that he had been starving.
